Package: bayespca
Title: A Package for Estimating PCA with Variational Bayes Inference
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Davide Vidotto 
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Davide Vidotto
Maintainer: Davide Vidotto <d.vidotto@uvt.nl>
Description: Bayesian estimation of weight vectors in PCA.
             To achieve regularization, the method allows specifying fixed precisions
             in the prior distributions of the weights; alternatively, it is possible
             to specify Gamma priors for such parameters. The method allows
             for variable selection through Automatic Relevance Determination.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
